text: Heike Holstein (born 10 December 1971) is an Irish equestrian. She competed at the 1996 Summer Olympics, the 2000 Summer Olympics and the 2004 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Irish female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Ireland Category:Equestrians at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 2004 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Dublin (city)
